## ðŸ‡ºðŸ‡¸ English

Study project written in pure PHP.  
The goal is to understand how frameworks like Laravel work internally â€” routing, controllers, basic CLI, and a small embedded server.

No frameworks used. Everything is built from scratch in a simple and educational way.

### Current features
- Basic router (GET/POST)
- Simple controller structure
- `miniartisan` CLI (run, routes, help)
- PHP built-in development server
- Minimal micro-framework-style layout

### Purpose
Learn the core pieces behind a modern PHP framework and improve architectural understanding.
